tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE equipment_inventory (
    equipment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    equipment_name VARCHAR(50),
    weight DECIMAL,
    quantity INT,
    location VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE CrossFitClasses (
    class_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    class_name VARCHAR(50),
    instructor VARCHAR(50),
    time_start TIME,
    time_end TIME
);

CREATE TABLE weights (
  weight_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  weight_name VARCHAR(50),
  weight_size VARCHAR(20),
  weight_quantity INT
)

CREATE TABLE ropes (
  rope_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  rope_type VARCHAR(50),
  rope_length INT,
  rope_color VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE mats (
  mat_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  mat_type VARCHAR(50),
  mat_height INT,
  mat_width INT
)
